title: MOBILEMATE MicroSD / MicroSDHC / Memory Stick Micro M2 USB 2.0 Card Reader / Writer supports upto 16GB MicroSDHC and 16GB M2
description: New SanDisk 2.0 USB High Speed MobileMate Micro Reader . Model # SDDR-121-A11M. Transferring music, video, photos and personal data between your digital devices and your USB compatible PC while on the go is faster and more convenient with SanDisk's MobileMate Readers. Ideal for memory-enabled mobile phone users and photo travel needs, the flash memory cards can be plugged directly into the readers. No card adapters are required. And they're so compact; they can fit in your pocket. Now, how easy is that? . *Does NOT include a flash memory card. No additional driver installation required for Windows ME, 2000, XP, Vista and Mac OS X.. High-speed USB 2.0 MobileMate Micro Reader. ; Compatible With:.
